Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.00,0:01:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵 是不是发生了什么好事啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.57,0:01:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？怎么这样问？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.51,0:01:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为总觉得葵好像很高兴的样子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.08,0:01:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是这样吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.95,0:01:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？去买东西吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.95,0:02:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是想说如果可以的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.56,0:02:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天要不要跟我一起去？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.92,0:02:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 如果你还有其他事情要做就算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.56,0:02:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.40,0:02:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请务必让我跟您去 薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.40,0:02:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管怎样我都会去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.50,0:02:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.12,0:02:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天要穿什么去呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.96,0:02:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.18,0:03:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十五话  胸怀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.55,0:03:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 雅是要钿女的饲料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.22,0:03:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙子是要黑魔术小说的最新一集
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.89,0:03:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.56,0:03:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,电玩软体『FIGHTING童养婿Ⅲ』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.90,0:03:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个是格斗游戏…吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.90,0:03:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.47,0:03:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让您久等了 薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.78,0:03:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很漂亮的和服呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.52,0:03:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您中意吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.79,0:03:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常的好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.36,0:03:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十分适合呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.36,0:03:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.36,0:03:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常谢谢您 薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.86,0:03:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.64,0:03:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实这是奶奶留给我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.41,0:04:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦 是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.44,0:04:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那小葵是奶奶带大的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.61,0:04:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 我父母亲都很忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.85,0:04:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,常常麻烦她照顾我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.45,0:04:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是个非常温柔的人 我很喜欢她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.19,0:04:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然在五年前过世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.69,0:04:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.36,0:04:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了吗？小葵？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.37,0:04:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,樱花…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.57,0:04:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.91,0:04:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每到这时节我都会跟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.75,0:04:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶一起去看樱花呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.42,0:04:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个时候 奶奶一定都会穿这件和服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.59,0:04:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我因为很喜欢这件和服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.03,0:04:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以常常向奶奶吵着要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.53,0:05:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶 我也想要穿这件和服啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.87,0:05:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你喜欢和服胜过洋装呢 真不愧是和服店的女儿呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.81,0:05:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 我最…喜欢和服了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.11,0:05:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那葵 你要记住喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.41,0:05:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和服这个东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.42,0:05:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是会染上穿的人的心情与思念喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.25,0:05:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以穿上和服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.59,0:05:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就等于是披上了『和服的思念』喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.36,0:05:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,『和服的思念』？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.70,0:05:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这对现在的小葵来说太难懂了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.43,0:05:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.27,0:05:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵 你长大之后这个和服就送给你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.71,0:05:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.27,0:05:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后穿上它和将来会成为你伴侣的人一起走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.21,0:05:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个人我已经决定了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.32,0:05:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要跟花菱家的薰在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.42,0:05:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊 跟花菱家的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.09,0:05:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.09,0:06:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我年轻的时候 也常常跟你爷爷这样一起走着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.03,0:06:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爷爷他…很喜欢这件和服喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.54,0:06:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果这件和服的思念能够传达给你的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.94,0:06:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个叫花菱的孩子一定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.77,0:06:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定也会喜欢这件和服的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.15,0:06:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个时候 我虽然还不能理解奶奶说的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.75,0:06:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 现在我已经完全了解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.59,0:06:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这件和服染满了对所爱的人的思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.10,0:06:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很棒的话呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.01,0:06:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.54,0:06:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我穿了这件衣服之后 好像就愈来愈喜欢你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.82,0:07:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我总是想着有一天能穿着这件和服跟薰一起出门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.23,0:07:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊 总觉得有点不好意思呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.50,0:07:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 要买的东西差不多就这些吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.77,0:07:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.71,0:07:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰 这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.71,0:07:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您还记得吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.55,0:07:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里…啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.35,0:07:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 这里是我跟小葵相会的地方呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.39,0:07:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.05,0:07:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那时偶然碰见的薰还把我坏的木屐带修好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.26,0:07:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.23,0:07:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平时我是不会做这种事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.16,0:07:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是不知道为什么 那个时候很在意你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.40,0:07:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？咦？为什么过不去呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.07,0:07:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.44,0:07:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,该怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.08,0:08:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个 请问怎么了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.71,0:08:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.32,0:08:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常谢谢你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.72,0:08:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总觉得好像看到了那个时候的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.49,0:08:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 你还记得后来我们搭电车时候的事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.73,0:08:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是现在想想 好像很快就到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.90,0:08:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实那个时候小葵睡着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.67,0:08:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到站的时候 电车已经往返一圈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.54,0:08:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？是这样子吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.11,0:08:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.71,0:08:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我太安心了 精神一下子就放松
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.62,0:08:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个…只有这样吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.62,0:08:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是不是还做了其他让您困扰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.22,0:08:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其他…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.72,0:08:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个…像是说梦话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.96,0:08:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梦话是没有 但是流了一些口水呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.30,0:08:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,骗你的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.23,0:08:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰您真是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.34,0:09:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我那时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.31,0:09:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到东京来的时候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.31,0:09:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.78,0:09:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.35,0:09:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.89,0:09:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个…小葵 要去看看吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.56,0:09:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到哪里去？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.22,0:09:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,公寓…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.89,0:09:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个我之前住的公寓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.73,0:09:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.64,0:09:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全没变呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.64,0:09:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去房间看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.24,0:09:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.94,0:09:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像没人住的样子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.29,0:09:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,门开着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.87,0:10:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好怀念啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.20,0:10:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也很怀念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.87,0:10:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为这个房子里有许多无法忘却的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.85,0:10:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.82,0:10:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有的时候会做梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.25,0:10:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.49,0:10:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.99,0:10:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这个房间里跟薰一起生活的梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.19,0:11:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是在梦里的薰一句话都不说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.43,0:11:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我无论说什么你都不发一语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.27,0:11:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我为了那样的薰做料理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.11,0:11:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.61,0:11:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请用餐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.54,0:11:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我尝试着想做些什么让你打起精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.55,0:11:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起看电视 一起看书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.52,0:11:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起谈着快乐的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.42,0:11:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想要让你打起精神来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.65,0:11:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是薰还是不发一语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.53,0:11:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我完全不知如何是好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.66,0:11:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就想我也许被薰您讨厌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.33,0:11:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,觉得非常的悲伤 眼泪夺眶而出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.84,0:11:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后我总是在这个时候醒过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.61,0:11:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我注意到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.21,0:11:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的在睡着的时候流眼泪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.48,0:11:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明是梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.38,0:11:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明只是梦而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.65,0:12:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不安扩散到了整个胸口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.09,0:12:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.16,0:12:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.00,0:12:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.10,0:12:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说了奇怪的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.10,0:12:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定是自己太爱担心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.01,0:12:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.88,0:12:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没这回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.61,0:12:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没这…回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.88,0:12:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个…薰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.39,0:12:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.39,0:12:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟妈妈分开之后在花菱家的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.50,0:12:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都只有些痛苦的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.56,0:12:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快乐的事情一件都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.23,0:12:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相当的憎恨花菱家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.00,0:12:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,母亲过世之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.57,0:12:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要想到自己身体里流着花菱家的血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.61,0:12:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就觉得自己快疯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.55,0:13:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最后我终于存了点钱 离开了花菱家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.32,0:13:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后来到东京一个人生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.39,0:13:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住在这间公寓里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.49,0:13:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后每天打工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.40,0:13:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是为了不依靠任何人生活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.90,0:13:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为没有可以依靠的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.07,0:13:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这个房间里孤单一个人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.40,0:13:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我第一次体会到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.21,0:13:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在这个世上…已经没有称之为家人的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.21,0:13:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我之前还一直诅咒着自己的出生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.62,0:13:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.12,0:13:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是这样的我只有一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.22,0:13:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令我觉得我能出生花菱家真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.56,0:13:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是…小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.13,0:13:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能跟你相会 能有你这个未婚妻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.97,0:13:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我有生以来唯一的救赎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.61,0:14:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.65,0:14:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是我的未婚妻真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.68,0:14:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜欢你 小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.73,0:14:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 但是如果薰是喜欢上和服…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.63,0:14:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而不是喜欢我的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.40,0:14:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系 不用担心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.47,0:14:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果和服的思念能够传达给葵的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.47,0:14:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵的思念一定也能传达给那个花菱家的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.61,0:14:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后他一定能够回应你的思念的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.85,0:14:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好高兴 我好高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.35,0:14:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰你第一次…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.96,0:14:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次对我说你喜欢我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.36,0:15:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的心情终于传达给薰您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.97,0:15:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.90,0:15:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 我一直一直都很不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.74,0:15:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然我以未婚妻的身份陪在您的身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.45,0:15:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我一直不知道薰您是怎么看待我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.45,0:15:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的心情 真的能传达给薰您吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.69,0:15:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好几次都想问您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.36,0:15:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是很害怕您会怎么样回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.96,0:15:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.73,0:15:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.53,0:15:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是要再说一次我会有点害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.37,0:15:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请不要向我道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.04,0:15:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰您没有任何错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.41,0:15:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啊 我真是太爱担心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.51,0:15:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在小时候和薰您见面后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.02,0:15:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是一直自己烦恼、不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.89,0:15:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰您现在在做什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.13,0:16:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,过着什么样的生活呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.46,0:16:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,变成什么样的人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.03,0:16:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就是一直想着你的事一遍长大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.87,0:16:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是突然听到了那件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.24,0:16:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么？为什么会取消？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.08,0:16:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,理由并没有说明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.25,0:16:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花菱家只说 这份婚约已经取消了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.35,0:16:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是花菱家说的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.92,0:16:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是薰说的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.82,0:16:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有听花菱家这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.09,0:16:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 这并不是薰他自己决定的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.70,0:16:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵大小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.60,0:16:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这份婚约已经结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.70,0:16:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您的心情我很了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.54,0:16:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是您跟花菱家已经没有婚约了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.31,0:16:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.84,0:16:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵大小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.08,0:16:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不要！我不要！我不要！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.25,0:16:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就是因为薰才努力至今的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.85,0:17:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是为了能陪在薰的身边才努力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.25,0:17:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我除了薰以外的人都不会考虑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.03,0:17:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵大小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.10,0:17:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那之后 我不断的哭着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.20,0:17:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像要把眼泪流干的一直哭着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.20,0:17:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后我决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.44,0:17:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要到薰您的身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.04,0:17:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我不知道薰您变成了什么样的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.64,0:17:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以非常的不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.81,0:17:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是知道帮助了我的人就是薰您的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.42,0:17:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.59,0:17:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为薰跟我想的一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.42,0:17:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 是比我想像中还棒的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.76,0:17:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰您是我的未婚夫真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.83,0:17:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你 小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.31,0:17:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最喜欢你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.98,0:18:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最喜欢你了 薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.65,0:18:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.32,0:18:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.85,0:18:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是个好地方喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.26,0:18:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,采光很棒又很安静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.09,0:18:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且又是最旁边的房间 应该不用我多说了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.00,0:18:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么样呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.17,0:18:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比想像中的还漂亮呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.97,0:18:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是没有另外的小房间有点…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.60,0:18:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种价格是理所当然的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.77,0:18:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我觉得木质地板比较好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.54,0:18:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我倒是喜欢和室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.38,0:18:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.81,0:18:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美你喜欢和室的话 那就好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.02,0:18:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的？太好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.38,0:18:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.88,0:18:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是两个人住会不会太窄了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.39,0:18:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种事我完全不在意啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.39,0:18:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为可以一直在阿隆身边啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.99,0:18:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样…这样吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.56,0:18:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错 没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.00,0:18:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由阿隆在的话 无论在哪里我都很幸福喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.57,0:18:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,房间虽然算不上大 但收纳的地方是不小的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.84,0:18:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收纳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.87,0:19:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看 怎么样啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.87,0:19:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以公寓来说算是大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.81,0:19:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经不在了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.04,0:19:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仲介先生 这里已经看完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.21,0:19:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,带我们去下一家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.38,0:19:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.92,0:19:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这东西是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.49,0:19:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.56,0:19:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁现在赶快出去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.66,0:19:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.50,0:19:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才那两个人会住那房间吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.74,0:19:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 也许吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.74,0:19:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总觉得有点羡慕他们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.38,0:19:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雅 蒂娜 妙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.45,0:19:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟大家在一起是很快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.28,0:19:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.29,0:19:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还是想跟你一起住在…能陪在你身边的房间啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.29,0:19:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.00,0:20:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 因为我就在小葵的身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.80,0:20:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不用再担心了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.97,0:20:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.47,0:20:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要 我要担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.97,0:20:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我是喜欢担心的人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.28,0:20:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今后我还要一直担心你的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.18,0:20:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为思念重要的人的心情是停止不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.68,0:20:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.69,0:20:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以说可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.45,0:20:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以更加更加担心你的事、更让你伤脑筋吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.53,0:20:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您讨厌这样子的我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.53,0:20:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜欢喔 小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.03,0:20:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.58,0:20:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.91,0:20:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们回去吧 小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.52,0:20:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.92,0:20:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰 我最喜欢你了
