Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.67,0:21:11.67,SongChnED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想念着你 想念着你 在该回去的时候却回不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.67,0:21:18.37,SongChnED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流着眼泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.67,0:21:27.17,SongChnED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵架了 无法见面 却想跟你见面 使我无法入眠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.37,0:21:34.67,SongChnED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恋爱总是反反复复
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.67,0:21:43.87,SongChnED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然常见却无法忘却
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.37,0:21:51.67,SongChnED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算不是特别的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.07,0:21:55.97,SongChnED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也买朵花吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.07,0:22:07.17,SongChnED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在蓝天中漂浮着在白云中生长的红花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.17,0:22:14.87,SongChnED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后跟你相会 让它伴随着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.87,0:22:26.67,SongChnED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使是微小又简单的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.15,0:22:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太过分了！太过分了！太过分了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.22,0:22:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰欺负我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.32,0:22:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有我的游戏没有买
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.46,0:22:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？奇怪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.82,0:22:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对 就是那里 去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.99,0:22:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,童养婿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.96,0:22:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管怎样我可不能输给童养婿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.17,0:22:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,（童养婿）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.84,0:22:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿嘿 我是水无月千夏喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.01,0:22:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要好好谈个恋爱才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.01,0:22:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样做 那样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.74,0:23:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后男人就会高兴 这书上也有写
